{"tid":1528270,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[港鐵呼籲] 唔好放孔明燈","createTime":"2019-09-01T13:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T13:50:05.000Z","uid":158996,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de74c8435a161c54d15adf9eaa5e33c58297287a","tid":1528270,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:27:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QXkH__YTIrw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQXkH__YTIrw&d=3Z9ZeYaQzwHPi2iIp4702PjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=dcdf110a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QXkH__YTIrw</a><br />\n<br />\n中秋佳節臨近，政府特意提醒市民唔好放孔明燈，因為唔知孔明燈放完會飛去邊，墜落嚟嘅火種會影響黨鐵運作，可能危害公眾安全。<br />\n<br />\n大家千祈<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span>咁做<br />\n<br />\n大家千祈<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span>咁做<br />\n<br />\n大家千祈<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span>咁做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869328808ef339d83fc2d6eea4c1ce4f00162d85","tid":1528270,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:28:13.000Z","msg":"但我地需要你關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[推上熱門］［92 &amp; 93］中學生為我地上前線 我地一齊聲援中學生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1527952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1527952</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0VUpjiC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0VUpjiC.jpg&h=9cea0167&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bbd4f4716cc73c31bc005c09ce4659b5c6cfd53","tid":1528270,"uid":44454,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"你想破壞港鐵嘅打爛嗰啲入閘機咪得囉， 放孔明燈隨時引起山火都唔知為乜， 唔好咁撚戇鳩啦"},{"pid":"93b4e1410e9edf3f90ac78d9ddad583eeeeda19d","tid":1528270,"uid":158996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:29:23.000Z","msg":"唉屌開錯台添<br />\n<br />\n不過孔明燈跌咗落路軌真係會影響上班<br />\n<br />\n所以大家千祈唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0528ae516aaba9faf7af323857cd755c5c2b3e1","tid":1528270,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7bbd4f4716cc73c31bc005c09ce4659b5c6cfd53","tid":1528270,"uid":44454,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"你想破壞港鐵嘅打爛嗰啲入閘機咪得囉， 放孔明燈隨時引起山火都唔知為乜， 唔好咁撚戇鳩啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:30:36.000Z","msg":"對唔撚住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acfaf374ceb3ea1d10c898c0235634c430b61df","tid":1528270,"uid":258402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:33:40.000Z","msg":"哎呀聽日要翻工，哎呀我冇地鐵會翻唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca448b3de7d1c83fd9807f0ade76d72626f38d88","tid":1528270,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:41:32.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"27a068dccc26b395f4486e0936b33db852a4023c","tid":1528270,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:41:43.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"9da612b2367d7509ad3a2663e085f333103f3fb7","tid":1528270,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:41:53.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"3bef23d98234e145db19f14781d60e29421c4e08","tid":1528270,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:42:05.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"d7fb7fb8ff5024c6bb756c376ea62f243e9819b7","tid":1528270,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:42:16.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"049db065b38a207f838299ae7a8294c238cec796","tid":1528270,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:42:27.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"bac6604bb81f7fe03fca761c52568af7dec8929e","tid":1528270,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:42:39.000Z","msg":"革"},{"pid":"3e9a79